lol.c:3:55: note: in definition of macro ‘ALIGN_VALUE_PTR’
    3 | #define ALIGN_VALUE_PTR(val) (&amp;((const typeof(val)) { val }))
      |                                                       ^~~

```

I&#39;m wondering if anyone has a better idea than what I have come up with.

